<li>"<a href="/wiki/Tonight_Quintet" title="Tonight Quintet">Tonight (Quintet &amp; Chorus)</a>"</li></ul>
</div></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style="width:1%">Act 2</th><td class="navbox-list-with-group navbox-list navbox-odd" style="width:100%;padding:0"><div style="padding:0 0.25em">
<ul><li>"<a href="/wiki/I_Feel_Pretty" title="I Feel Pretty">I Feel Pretty</a>"</li>
